{"tid":356281,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖) 係大陸農業銀行買黃金竟然生鏽,痴撚線？","createTime":"2017-08-12T03:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T03:15:22.000Z","uid":82845,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b10c40117b1b8c3c73fa86ed5cb2008399d9dd","tid":356281,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:11:12.000Z","msg":"有冇持實物金既巴絲打分享下係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/110646_eff7fe6d9fda62d16fe4cad9667f0008.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F110646_eff7fe6d9fda62d16fe4cad9667f0008.JPG&h=6c544eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/110652_fae5764d11f158e66824abbc8dd0382d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F110652_fae5764d11f158e66824abbc8dd0382d.JPG&h=8e3678a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/110655_f12713c91c4d477c4b1160c6167f7783.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F110655_f12713c91c4d477c4b1160c6167f7783.JPG&h=ab3324a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從2011年開始連續幾年在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">深圳農業銀行海王支行</span></span></strong>購買了虎年、龍年、兔年的&quot;生肖金&quot;（含量是4個9），每塊20克到60克不等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">買的時候農行告知最好不要拆包裝</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為如果以後要回收的話，拆了包裝就不能回購了。所以這金塊從買來什麼樣就一直原樣存著，沒拆過,和在商場買的金鍊等放一起。<br />\n<br />\n      去年心血來潮想看看金塊，竟然發現有幾塊生肖金&quot;生鏽&quot;了。但同時一起放的金鍊等沒有任何變化。去問農行，答覆說是真貨，生產的過程中有問題。想問問大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">4個9的黃金</span>會生鏽嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 轉貼<br />\n<br />\n大陸連銀行賣既野都係假? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313163e3e994f0ba80dd6c95305e8788df42ada8","tid":356281,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:12:34.000Z","msg":"中國特色既黃金"},{"pid":"ca6ac298baa05f1226099aa1a781086b7b741e9e","tid":356281,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"幻覺"},{"pid":"26d8c4e0f9f98b08667ed63b89514f78a1af01ed","tid":356281,"uid":35651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:13:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2763a7466b5cc079ab599bc8ced42849f884951","tid":356281,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"Fe 9999"},{"pid":"38fd437e8faa7af6360e02f68c32c41425071211","tid":356281,"uid":21149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"因為銀行係假既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f137e9b7126bcd1716f2fe2dc0b517ae7ec0210","tid":356281,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:15:11.000Z","msg":"應該係呢間分行成間都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c846b358b973749937ed78736835119497a56a36","tid":356281,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:15:22.000Z","msg":"大陸只有假貨同騙子係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}